Senior/Sales Engineer (Rosemount) (SALES-RMT/201312/01/SG)
Job ID
EPM-00006191
Country
Singapore
State/Province
Singapore
City
Singapore
Publish Start Date
Dec 19 2013
Job Level
Experienced (Non-Manager)
|
Responsibilities:
Pursue projects and grow the Rosemount business.
Identify opportunities, engage and close orders, with major EPC’s, skid vendors and OEM’s.
Pursuits cover both in-country projects as well as multinational projects destination to Singapore.
Influence key specifications in projects to strengthen position to win.
Provide feedback and market input to the Marketing team on competitive landscape eg., feature and price.
Work with sales support team and project management team for order processing, project documentation and service team to ensure service requests are met.
Involve Product Marketing team to support pursuits and manage cross border pursuits.
Requirements:
Diploma / Degree in Engineering with 3 years or more of sales experience in the process industry.
Experience in Oil & Gas, Refining, Petrochemicals, Chemicals, Power would be beneficial.
Good analytical and questioning skills coupled with ability to develop and implement sales strategies.
Strong in interpersonal and communication skills, especially influencing skills.